== 教育 ==
[[File:Gusana.jpg|thumb]]
根據[[國家統計研究所_(意大利)|國家統計研究所(Istat)]]於2001年所進行的普查，64歲以下人口的識字率為99.5%, 而總體識字率(包含65歲以上的群體)為98.2%。男性文盲比例(65歲以下)為0.24%而女性為0.25%。<ref name="edscuola.it">http://www.edscuola.it/archivio/statistiche/analfabetismo_01.pdf {{Wayback|url=http://www.edscuola.it/archivio/statistiche/analfabetismo_01.pdf |date=20200702231541 }} Analfabetismo Italia – Censimento 2001</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sardegnastatistiche.it/index.php?xsl=672&s=12&v=9&c=5042&subnodo=337&refp=0&id=251&tt=4&anno=5|title=Sardegna Statistiche – Statistiche  – Consulta le statistiche  – Argomenti|publisher=|access-date=2018-04-06|archive-date=2020-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217030114/http://www.sardegnastatistiche.it/index.php?xsl=672&s=12&v=9&c=5042&subnodo=337&refp=0&id=251&tt=4&anno=5|dead-url=no}}</ref>女性完成高等教育的比例則比男性高出10到20%。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sardegnastatistiche.it/index.php?xsl=672&s=12&v=9&c=5042&subnodo=337&refp=1&id=150&ss=1&modalita=tutte&tt=4|title=Sardegna Statistiche – Statistiche  – Consulta le statistiche  – Argomenti|publisher=|access-date=2018-04-06|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113015312/http://www.sardegnastatistiche.it/index.php?xsl=672&s=12&v=9&c=5042&subnodo=337&refp=1&id=150&ss=1&modalita=tutte&tt=4|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sardegnastatistiche.it/index.php?xsl=672&s=12&v=9&c=5042&subnodo=337&refp=1&id=154&ss=1&modalita=tutte&tt=4|title=Sardegna Statistiche – Statistiche  – Consulta le statistiche  – Argomenti|publisher=|access-date=2018-04-06|archive-date=2020-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217030131/http://www.sardegnastatistiche.it/index.php?xsl=672&s=12&v=9&c=5042&subnodo=337&refp=1&id=154&ss=1&modalita=tutte&tt=4|dead-url=no}}</ref> 撒丁島的中輟率在義大利各省分中排名第二。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.repubblica.it/solidarieta/cooperazione/2017/04/03/news/bambini_ecco_quanto_contano_le_poverta_educative_sull_infanzia_in_italia-162095270//|title=Bambini, ecco quanto pesa la povertà educativa sull'infanzia in Italia|work=repubblica.it|access-date=2018-04-06|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731000425/https://www.repubblica.it/solidarieta/cooperazione/2017/04/03/news/bambini_ecco_quanto_contano_le_poverta_educative_sull_infanzia_in_italia-162095270/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

撒丁島上有兩所公立大學，{{le|University of Sassari}}與{{le|University of Cagliari}}，分別成立於16和17世紀。2008年當地共有48979名學生就讀於此。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sardegnastatistiche.it/index.php?xsl=672&s=12&v=9&c=5042&subnodo=337&refp=1&id=152&tt=4&anno=45|title=Sardegna Statistiche – Statistiche  – Consulta le statistiche  – Argomenti|publisher=|access-date=2018-04-06|archive-date=2020-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025074614/http://www.sardegnastatistiche.it/index.php?xsl=672&s=12&v=9&c=5042&subnodo=337&refp=1&id=152&tt=4&anno=45|dead-url=no}}</ref>

